OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781046185
OL,3,CWhite working-class boys most let down
OL,4,Cby education system, new figures show
OL,6,FWhy is it so hard being a white
OL,7,Fworking class boy in Britain? Watch
OL,8,Four documentary from Gateshead
OL,10,FBy Senior Westminster Producer Maya
OL,11,FBowles and Westminster Reporter Lewis
OL,12,FDenison
OL,14,FAnti-social behaviour is high,
OL,15,Fopportunity is low, and there is
OL,16,Fnothing to do.
OL,18,FThat's what young people in Gateshead
OL,19,Ftold me about growing up in the north
OL,20,Feast of England as a white working-
OL,21,Fclass boy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781046185
OL,3,CWhite working-class boys most let down
OL,4,Cby education system, new figures show
OL,6,FThey are the demographic most let down
OL,7,Fby the system, according to the
OL,8,Fgovernment - and new statistics shared
OL,9,Fexclusively with ITV News as part of a
OL,10,Fmajor inquiry back that up.
OL,12,FWhite working-class kids are twice as
OL,13,Flikely to be absent from school,
OL,14,Faccording to the Independent Inquiry
OL,15,Finto White Working Class Educational
OL,16,FOutcomes.
OL,18,FOn average, pupils are missing 7% of
OL,19,Fschool lessons, compared to 13% for
OL,20,Fwhite working-class pupils.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781046185
OL,3,CWhite working-class boys most let down
OL,4,Cby education system, new figures show
OL,6,FWhite working-class kids are also two
OL,7,Fand a half times more likely to be
OL,8,Fseverely absent, meaning they're
OL,9,Fmissing more than 50% of school.
OL,11,FThe inquiry also found that white
OL,12,Fworking-class pupils are much more
OL,13,Flikely to have special educational
OL,14,Fneeds; 34% have SEND, compared to just
OL,15,F19% for others.
OL,17,FThe data will form part of a broader
OL,18,Freport into the attainment gap between
OL,19,Fwhite working-class kids and their
OL,20,Fpeers, due to be released at the end
OL,21,Fof June.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781046185
OL,3,CWhite working-class boys most let down
OL,4,Cby education system, new figures show
OL,6,FYoung men we spoke to explained why
OL,7,Fthey think it's so tough for working-
OL,8,Fclass boys in north east towns, but
OL,9,FEducation Secretary Bridget Phillipson
OL,10,Fadmitted to us she does not have all
OL,11,Fthe answers.
OL,13,FAll four we spoke to conveyed a sense
OL,14,Fof hopelessness among white working-
OL,15,Fclass boys in Gateshead, many of whom
OL,16,Fdon't care about passing their school
OL,17,Fexams because they see no future in
OL,18,Fmeaningful employment.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781046185
OL,3,CWhite working-class boys most let down
OL,4,Cby education system, new figures show
OL,6,FBut despite their tough experiences,
OL,7,Fall have now found light at the end of
OL,8,Fa long, dark tunnel.
OL,10,FEric, 18, is now training to be a
OL,11,Fyouth worker after missing most of
OL,12,Fschool following the murder of his
OL,13,Fbest friend, Tomasz Oleszak, when they
OL,14,Fwere both just 14.
OL,16,FHe explained how his attendance fell
OL,17,Fto just 14% by the time he left
OL,18,Fschool, and he'd lost interest in
OL,19,Fpassing his exams.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781046185
OL,3,CWhite working-class boys most let down
OL,4,Cby education system, new figures show
OL,6,F"I didn't have the greatest of
OL,7,Fexperiences with school, and so in
OL,8,Fgeneral I was ill. After school, my
OL,9,Fwhole thing was - because I had had a
OL,10,Fbad experience with school - was 'I'm
OL,11,Fnot doing my GCSEs'," he said.
OL,13,F"And that was daft is to think like
OL,14,Fthat because you absolutely do."
OL,16,FEric says the youth work organisation
OL,17,Fhe is part of has given him a path to
OL,18,Ffulfilment by helping other young
OL,19,Fpeople get on the right track.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781046185
OL,3,CWhite working-class boys most let down
OL,4,Cby education system, new figures show
OL,6,FBut well over 1,000 youth clubs have
OL,7,Fclosed in the UK since 2010. Labour
OL,8,Fhas promised to reverse that trend,
OL,9,Fbut facilities are still closing.
OL,11,FLuke, 18, says his local youth club,
OL,12,Fwhich closed last week, "did a lot for
OL,13,Fme and all my friends that went there".
OL,15,F"It's just a good environment,
OL,16,Fespecially to keep us off the streets."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781046185
OL,3,CWhite working-class boys most let down
OL,4,Cby education system, new figures show
OL,6,FAsked what it will be like now the
OL,7,Fclub is closed for good, Luke said:
OL,8,F"Tough. Me and all my mates used to go
OL,9,Fdown on a Wednesday. You'd have like a
OL,10,Ftime to just basically breathe and not
OL,11,Fhave to worry about if someone's going
OL,12,Fto be following us - not have to worry
OL,13,Fabout basically the dangers."
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/19
