CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781046185
OL,3,CWhite working-class boys most let down
OL,4,Cby education system, new figures show
OL,6,FThe government has committed to
OL,7,Fopening dozens of youth hubs aimed at
OL,8,Fgiving young people support with jobs
OL,9,Fand wellbeing, in a bid to support
OL,10,Fworking class young people.
OL,12,FEight young futures hubs are set to
OL,13,Fopen in Birmingham, Brighton and Hove,
OL,14,FBristol, County Durham, Leeds,
OL,15,FManchester, Nottingham and Tower
OL,16,FHamlets.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781046185
OL,3,CWhite working-class boys most let down
OL,4,Cby education system, new figures show
OL,6,FThe youth centres will help young
OL,7,Fpeople aged up to 18 with employment
OL,8,Fadvice, health and wellbeing, and are
OL,9,Falso aimed at preventing them from
OL,10,Ffalling into a life of crime. The
OL,11,Ffirst wave will open in areas with
OL,12,Fhigh anti-social behaviour.
OL,14,FJunior, a 17 year old with visual
OL,15,Fimpairment, credits his youth worker
OL,16,Fwith saving his life amid a tough
OL,17,Fperiod of depression.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781046185
OL,3,CWhite working-class boys most let down
OL,4,Cby education system, new figures show
OL,6,F"I was missing education for two
OL,7,Fyears, 9 and 10. I wasn't barely in
OL,8,Fany of the time and if I was, I got
OL,9,Fsuspended the same day," he told me,
OL,10,Fsaying his teachers offered no support
OL,11,Fto help with his mental health.
OL,13,F"I nearly killed myself a few times,"
OL,14,Fhe said, until youth worker John found
OL,15,Fhim.
OL,17,F"Honestly, (he was) the best thing
OL,18,Fthat changed my life. If he wasn't
OL,19,Fthere, I know it's like, dramatic, but
OL,20,FI don't I don't think I'd be sitting
OL,21,Fhere without him," he said.
OL,26,@yD@LpmyD@Spn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781046185
OL,3,CWhite working-class boys most let down
OL,4,Cby education system, new figures show
OL,6,FAll the young people we spoke to said
OL,7,Fmore youth clubs and more mental
OL,8,Fhealth support at school would go some
OL,9,Fway toward improving the life chances
OL,10,Fof white working class boys.
OL,12,FThey are the demographic struggling
OL,13,Fthe most, but they are not far behind
OL,14,Ftheir female counterparts or working-
OL,15,Fclass pupils from ethnic minorities.
OL,17,FAsked how she could support white
OL,18,Fworking-class boys without fuelling a
OL,19,Fculture war, Education Secretary
OL,20,FPhillipson said the numbers show it's
OL,21,Fa necessary task.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781046185
OL,3,CWhite working-class boys most let down
OL,4,Cby education system, new figures show
OL,6,F"It is right that we set out the
OL,7,Fchallenge and the data is really clear
OL,8,Fthat white working-class kids get
OL,9,Famongst the worst outcomes in the
OL,10,Feducation system.
OL,12,F"That's not to say there aren't other
OL,13,Fdisparities, and we absolutely will
OL,14,Ftackle those too. One of the biggest
OL,15,Findicators is obviously class
OL,16,Fbackground and the amount of money
OL,17,Fthat your family has. "That's why
OL,18,Ftackling child poverty is such a big
OL,19,Fpriority for this government."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781046185
OL,3,CWhite working-class boys most let down
OL,4,Cby education system, new figures show
OL,6,FThe government has announced plans for
OL,7,FMission North East, to help working-
OL,8,Fclass people in the area, but it is
OL,9,Fnot yet clear exactly how it will
OL,10,Fachieve its aims.
OL,12,FAsked to explain, the education
OL,13,Fsecretary said: "We will be doing a
OL,14,Fkind of a formal launch of it and
OL,15,Fsetting out further plans on it. But I
OL,16,Fthink I do have to be honest in saying
OL,17,Fthat we do have some big ideas about
OL,18,Fthings we want to do to make this work
OL,19,Fbetter.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30715
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781046185
OL,3,CWhite working-class boys most let down
OL,4,Cby education system, new figures show
OL,6,F"But if we had all the answers, we
OL,7,Fwould have solved it by now."
OL,9,FAn academic who contributed to the
OL,10,Finquiry into white working-class
OL,11,Feducational outcomes said there are
OL,12,Ffour main areas for the government to
OL,13,Ftarget.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30716
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781046185
OL,3,CWhite working-class boys most let down
OL,4,Cby education system, new figures show
OL,6,FProfessor Lindsay Macmillan, Professor
OL,7,Fof Economics at University College
OL,8,FLondon, and the Founding Director of
OL,9,Fthe Centre for Education Policy and
OL,10,FEqualising Opportunities, said
OL,11,Fministers should consider improving
OL,12,Fthe early years abilities of white
OL,13,Fworking-class boys, because too many
OL,14,Fare arriving at primary school not
OL,15,Fready.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30717
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781046185
OL,3,CWhite working-class boys most let down
OL,4,Cby education system, new figures show
OL,6,FThe transition from primary school to
OL,7,Fsecondary school is a "key area" where
OL,8,Fwhite working-class boys become
OL,9,Fdisengaged with education and thirdly,
OL,10,Fshe said the government must improve
OL,11,Fpost-16 pathways.
OL,13,FShe said there needs to be a "clear
OL,14,Fline of sight from the education
OL,15,Fsystem to paths that come next
OL,16,Fthrough, linked to the local
OL,17,Fopportunities in the labour market".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30718
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781046185
OL,3,CWhite working-class boys most let down
OL,4,Cby education system, new figures show
OL,6,FFinally, Professor Macmillan said the
OL,7,Fgovernment needs to improve the school
OL,8,Fattendance of white working-class male
OL,9,Fstudents, which is far below that of
OL,10,Fother pupils.
OL,12,FShe denied it was impossible to
OL,13,Ftotally level the playing field, but
OL,14,Faccepted it would be tough.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30719
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1781046185
OL,3,CWhite working-class boys most let down
OL,4,Cby education system, new figures show
OL,6,FAsked if it would be impossible to
OL,7,Ftotally level the playing field across
OL,8,Fdemographics, she said: "That is one
OL,9,Fbleak take on our job and what we're
OL,10,Fdoing here. But I think that the more
OL,11,Foptimistic take would be you've got to
OL,12,Fstart somewhere and diagnosing the
OL,13,Fproblem so clearly across the system
OL,14,Fis a really important start."
OL,16,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,17,Four political experts are across all
OL,18,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,19,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/19
